snippet.title: Boom!
snippet.description:
Boom! is a turn-based PvP battle game in pixel art.
+150 destructible battlefields, +200 characters to unlock, +75 original weapons, Private Arenas, and much more.  
Boom! is FREE to play with nos ads. 

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/boom-online-pvp-battles/id1621701116
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onebutton.boom&hl=en&gl=US
